  "remarks": "CDi.010 FDLR Executive Secretary. Arrested in Paris on 3 October 2010 under ICC warrant for war crimes and crimes against humanity committed by FDLR troops in the Kivus in 2009. Transferred to The Hague on 25 January 2011and released by the ICC in late 2011. Elected FDLR Executive Secretary on 29 Nov. 2014 for a five-year term.; Listing: Listed by 1533 Committee on 3 Mar. 2009 (amended on 13 Oct. 2016)",
